						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying in front of the Karanam's house.</p>						

						<p>Gajapati: Bhānudēva, 14th year.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1287, Karkāṭaka, śu. 5. Friday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register the grant of land for providing food offerings to the god Sōmanātha by Nandanamahārāju. Mentions Mallinātha.</p>						

